1:54:02,340 --> 1:54:04,090
不用了
No.

1064
1:54:04,250 --> 1:54:06,920
他不是我找的那个人
He's not the one I want.

1065
1:54:08,670 --> 1:54:10,960
他不是什么?
He's not the what?

1066
1:54:11,130 --> 1:54:13,250
你知道我指的是什么
You know what I mean.

1067
1:54:13,420 --> 1:54:15,630
他在哪儿？
Where is he?

1068
1:54:15,800 --> 1:54:17,800
听着
Look...

1069
1:54:18,380 --> 1:54:22,920
迪克跟整件事没有关系 他以为你是我父亲
Dick has nothing to do with all that stuff.\nHe thinks you're my father.

1070
1:54:23,090 --> 1:54:25,340
请不要把事情搞那么复杂
Please don't bring up all that muck.

1071
1:54:27,090 --> 1:54:30,420
-好吧 我自己会搞清楚\n-你真不知道？
-All right, I'll find out myself.\n-You really don't know?

1072
1:54:37,670 --> 1:54:39,670
老天爷 爸爸 是奎尔第
My God, Dad, it was Quilty.

1073
1:54:39,840 --> 1:54:41,960
是克莱尔·奎尔第
It was Clare Quilty.

1074
1:54:50,090 --> 1:54:52,090
对
Yes.

1075
1:54:57,590 --> 1:54:59,710
是的 当然是他
Yes, of course.

1076
1:55:18,760 --> 1:55:20,550
奎尔第
Quilty.

1077
1:55:21,670 --> 1:55:23,670
是的
Yeah.\nYeah.

1078
1:55:25,880 --> 1:55:29,550
他是唯一的一个让我疯狂的男人
He was the only man\nI was ever really crazy about.

1079
1:55:34,340 --> 1:55:36,550
那我呢？
What about me?

1080
1:56:04,090 --> 1:56:06,090
他带你去哪儿了？
Where did he take you?

1081
1:56:10,130 --> 1:56:12,380
快点告诉我
Just tell me.

1082
1:56:13,590 --> 1:56:16,700
好吧 每个人都知道他喜欢小姑娘
Well, everybody knew he liked little girls.

1083
1:56:17,590 --> 1:56:21,470
他曾经在他在帕金顿的豪宅里把她们拍下来
He used to film them in his mansion\nover in Parkington, Pavor Manor.

1084
1:56:23,930 --> 1:56:27,090
但是我没有干那些事情
But I wasn't gonna do all those things.

1085
1:56:28,590 --> 1:56:30,590
什么事？
All what things?

1086
1:56:30,760 --> 1:56:32,840
两个男孩两个女孩或者
Two girls and two boys or...

1087
1:56:33,010 --> 1:56:35,090
我不清楚 大概三四个男人
..l don't know, three or four men.

1088
1:56:35,260 --> 1:56:37,720
另外 Vivian把整个过程拍下来
And Vivian was filming the whole thing.

1089
1:56:37,880 --> 1:56:41,720
我说“不 我才不会给这些禽兽男人们吹箫”
I said "No, I'm not gonna blow\nall those beastly boys."

1090
1:56:41,880 --> 1:56:44,010
“我想跟你”
"I want you."

1091
1:56:47,340 --> 1:56:49,220
所以她把我除外了
So he threw me out.

1092
1:56:58,970 --> 1:57:00,970
我看着她 看了又看
I looked and looked at her...

1093
1:57:03,010 --> 1:57:06,300
我知道 就像我知道我必死无疑那样清楚
..and I knew,\nas clearly as I know that I will die,...

1094
1:57:06,470 --> 1:57:11,050
我是如此的爱她 胜过我所看到的所能想象到的地球上的任何事物
..that I loved her more than anything\nI'd ever seen or imagined on earth.

1095
1:57:15,180 --> 1:57:19,140
她以前是一个妖女 现在却像一片枯叶
She was only the dead leaf echo\nof the nymphet from long ago...

1096
1:57:20,390 --> 1:57:22,760
但是我爱她 这个洛丽塔
..but I loved her, this Lolita,...

1097
1:57:22,930 --> 1:57:26,390
苍白、臃肿、混俗 怀着别的男人的孩子
..pale and polluted\nand big with another man's child.

1098
1:57:26,550 --> 1:57:29,720
她可以褪色 可以枯萎 我不在乎
She could fade and wither -I didn't care.

1099
1:57:31,720 --> 1:57:34,390
但我只要看她一眼
I would still go mad with tenderness...

1100
1:57:34,510 --> 1:57:36,510
万般柔情 涌上心头
..at the mere sight other face.

1101
1:58:00,010 --> 1:58:02,010
洛丽塔
Lolita...

1102
1:58:04,300 --> 1:58:08,390
从这里到那个你熟悉的汽车
From here to that old car\nthat you know so well...

1103
1:58:08,560 --> 1:58:10,810
只有25步的距离
..is a stretch of 25 paces.

1104
1:58:13,600 --> 1:58:16,100
走过这25步
Make those 25 steps...

1105
1:58:16,260 --> 1:58:18,260
跟我在一起吧
..with me, now.

1106
1:58:18,700 --> 1:58:22,850
你是说如果我跟你一起去汽车旅馆你就会给我点钱？
You're saying you'll give us some money\nif I go to a motel with you?

1107
1:58:23,010 --> 1:58:24,970
不是 不是！！
No... No!

1108
1:58:25,140 --> 1:58:29,640
我是说你离开这里和我一起生活 一起死去 和我一起干任何事
I'm saying leave here and come live\nwith me, die with me, everything with me.

1109
1:58:30,810 --> 1:58:32,810
你简直是疯了
You're crazy.

1110
1:58:32,970 --> 1:58:35,680
如果你拒绝你仍然能拿到这些钱
If you refuse, you still get the money.

1111
1:58:35,850 --> 1:58:37,260
-真的？\n-是的
-Really?\n-Yeah.

1112
1:58:39,060 --> 1:58:41,060
拿着 拿着吧
There. Have it.

1113
1:58:50,060 --> 1:58:51,930
哦 老天爷
Oh my God.

1114
1:58:52,100 --> 1:58:55,390
你给了我四千美元？
You're giving us four thousand bucks?

1115
1:58:58,640 --> 1:59:00,270
-谢谢\n-不要
-Thank you...\n-No...

1116
1:59:00,280 --> 1:59:01,000
不要碰我
Don't touch me.

1117
1:59:01,700 --> 1:59:04,600
你一碰我我就会死
I'll die if you touch me.

1118
1:59:05,930 --> 1:59:10,640
我只想告诉你\n你有机会跟我一起走
Just tell me...\nthere's a chance you'll come with me.

1119
1:59:12,700 --> 1:59:14,700
不 亲爱的
No, honey.

1120
1:59:14,600 --> 1:59:16,930
我宁愿跟克莱尔走
I'd almost rather go back with Clare.

1121
1:59:20,390 --> 1:59:22,390
噢
Oh...

1122
1:59:22,560 --> 1:59:24,560
好了 我走了
I'll go now.

1123
1:59:26,680 --> 1:59:31,020
-我让迪克回来跟你告别？\n-不用了 我根本不想见他
-Can I call Dick in to say goodbye?\n-No. I don't want to see him, at all.

1124
1:59:31,180 --> 1:59:34,230
我只想走
I just want to go.

1125
1:59:43,680 --> 1:59:46,890
洛 你能不能忘记我对你做过的事情？
Lo, can you ever forget\nwhat I've done to you?

1126
1:59:52,060 --> 1:59:54,060
说再见 莫利
Say goodbye, Molly.

1127
1:59:55,140 --> 1:59:57,140
跟爸爸说再见
Say goodbye to my dad.

1128
2:01:04,350 --> 2:01:06,440
迪克！你猜有什么好消息！
Dick! Guess what!

1129
2:01:27,350 --> 2:01:29,690
陪审团的先生女士们
Ladies and gentlemen of the jury,...

1130
2:01:29,850 --> 2:01:34,770
我必须说我对在煤山那次告别以前所作的事感到后悔
..l have to say that I regret all I did\nbefore that last goodbye in Coalmont.

1131
2:01:36,810 --> 2:01:40,400
但我从来不对后来发生的事后悔
But I regret nothing of what came after.

1132
2:03:16,280 --> 2:03:18,280
哦 你是谁？
Now, who are you?

1133
2:03:22,070 --> 2:03:24,150
你是 是不是布鲁斯特？
Are you, by any chance, Brewster?

1134
2:03:30,530 --> 2:03:33,320
你知道不 你看起来不像杰克 布鲁斯特
You know, you don't look\nlike Jack Brewster.

1135
2:03:33,480 --> 2:03:36,980
我是说 神似并不让人感到意外
I mean, the resemblance\nis not particularly striking.

1136
2:03:37,150 --> 2:03:41,650
有人说他有个兄弟有一个同样的电话公司
Somebody told me he had a brother\nwith the same phone company.

1137
2:03:41,820 --> 2:03:07,820
我不是什么布鲁斯特兄弟
I'm neither of the Brewsters.

1138
2:03:50,860 --> 2:03:52,360
到路边停下
Pull over!

1139
2:03:53,440 --> 2:03:54,940
到路边停下
Pull over!

1140
2:03:58,150 --> 2:04:00,570
你记不记得有个小女孩名字叫
Do you recall a little girl named...

1141
2:04:02,400 --> 2:04:04,190
多丽丝·海兹？
..Dolores Haze?

1142
2:04:08,400 --> 2:04:10,820
你晓得不 我是她父亲
You see, I'm her father.

1143
2:04:12,200 --> 2:04:13,690
瞎扯
Nonsense.

1144
2:04:13,860 --> 2:04:17,320
你是外国人 你是外国势力的特工
You're a foreigner.\nYou're an agent of a foreign power.

1145
2:04:17,490 --> 2:04:19,570
你是个外国文化特工
You're a foreign literary agent.

1146
2:04:19,740 --> 2:04:22,150
她是我女儿
She was my daughter.

1147
2:04:22,320 --> 2:04:24,320
她是我孩子
She was my child.

1148
2:04:24,490 --> 2:04:26,860
哦 你知道 我喜欢孩子们
Oh, you know, I adore children myself.

1149
2:04:27,030 --> 2:04:29,030
也喜欢他们的父亲
And fathers...

1150
2:04:29,200 --> 2:04:31,240
我喜欢父亲
I love fathers.

1151
2:04:34,780 --> 2:04:36,570
啊
Ah...

1152
2:04:36,740 --> 2:04:37,700
坐下！
Sit down!

1153
2:04:39,400 --> 2:04:41,400
哦 找到了
Oh. There they are.

1154
2:04:41,570 --> 2:04:42,820
现在我需要一些火柴 借个火？
Now we need matches. You got a light?

1155
2:04:44,990 --> 2:04:46,570
奎尔第 你给我集中精神
Quilty, I want you to concentrate.

1156
2:04:49,950 --> 2:04:51,610
你马上就要死
You're about to die.

1157
2:04:51,780 --> 2:04:54,110
喔
Ooh.

1158
2:05:02,070 --> 2:05:03,650
耶稣
Jesus!

1159
2:05:05,030 --> 2:05:09,320
你想站着死还是坐着死？
Do you want to be executed\nstanding up or sitting down?

1160
2:05:09,490 --> 2:05:12,910
让我想想 让我想想 这是个很难回答的问题
Just let me think, let me think.\nIt's not an easy question.

1161
2:05:13,070 --> 2:05:15,530
我只想知道发生了什么事
Try to understand what is happening.

1162
2:05:15,700 --> 2:05:16,530
我 我 我我
I-l-l-l...

1163
2:05:16,700 --> 2:05:20,070
-记得多丽丝·海兹？\n-我愿意
-Remember Dolores Haze.\n-I'm willing...

1164
2:05:20,240 --> 2:05:23,570
我愿意试试 我 只是
I'm willing to try. I am. Just...

1165
2:05:23,740 --> 2:05:25,410
好吧 听着
OK. Listen.

1166
2:05:25,570 --> 2:05:27,570
我犯了个错误 我很后悔
I made a mistake, which I regret,...

1167
2:05:27,740 --> 2:05:29,660
真的
..sincerely.

1168
2:05:29,820 --> 2:05:35,320
我跟多丽之间什么都没发生 实际上 我性无能
I couldn't have any fun with your Dolly.\nI'm practically impotent is the sad truth.

1169
2:05:35,490 --> 2:05:40,200
但是她有个很棒的假期 见到了很多不错的人 嘿 你知道吧-
But she had a swell vacation, met some\nremarkable people. Hey, do you know -

1170
2:05:54,910 --> 2:05:56,370
站好别动！
Stay still!

1171
2:05:58,070 --> 2:06:00,030
噢 老天爷
Oh, God...

1172
2:06:00,860 --> 2:06:02,860
你骗了我
You cheated me.

1173
2:06:05,490 --> 2:06:07,490
你欺骗了我的救赎
You cheated me of my redemption.

1174
2:06:09,990 --> 2:06:13,660
-你必须得死\n-我不知道你在说什么
-You have to die.\n-I don't know what you're talking about.

1175
2:06:13,820 --> 2:06:17,660
我的大脑和舌头今天有点不听使唤
My memory and my eloquence\nare not at their best today.

1176
2:06:17,820 --> 2:06:22,160
但是真的 你必须承认你从来不是一个理想的继父
But really, you have to admit\nyou were never an ideal stepfather.

1177
2:06:22,320 --> 2:06:24,320
嗯？
Hm?

1178
2:06:24,490 --> 2:06:26,950
我没有强迫你的女儿加入我们
I did not force your protégée to join me.

1179
2:06:27,120 --> 2:06:30,120
是她让我把她带到一个快乐的家中
It was she who made me\nremove her to a happier home.

1180
2:06:30,280 --> 2:06:32,570
看看你四周 看到了吗？
Look around you. See?

1181
2:06:32,740 --> 2:06:34,740
你看到这座房子了？
You see this house?

1182
2:06:34,910 --> 2:06:39,490
夏天很凉快 很舒服 我建议你搬进来 嗯？
It's very cool in the summer. Comfortable.\nI suggest that you move in, hm?

1183
2:06:42,330 --> 2:06:44,530
我想你住在这里一定很开心
I think you'll be happy here.

1184
2:06:45,620 --> 2:06:47,620
你可以用我的衣柜
You can use my wardrobe.

1185
2:06:48,580 --> 2:06:51,740
我们有最可信赖的的女佣
We have the most reliable\nand bribable charwoman.

1186
2:06:51,910 --> 2:06:54,370
“清洁女工” 是一个美国式条款
"Cleaning lady" is the American term.

1187
2:06:54,530 --> 2:06:58,120
她不仅有女儿 还有孙女
She has not only daughters,\nshe has granddaughters.

1188
2:06:58,280 --> 2:07:01,580
我还知道一两个关于警察局长的事
And I know a thing or two\nabout the chief of police...

1189
2:07:01,740 --> 2:07:03,780
让他成为我的奴隶的事
..that makes him my slave.

1190
2:07:03,950 --> 2:07:06,030
我的奴隶 把枪扔掉
My slave. Drop the gun.

1191
2:07:06,200 --> 2:07:08,700
还有件事 把枪扔掉
And here's another thing. Drop the gun.

1192
2:07:08,870 --> 2:07:12,740
就在楼上 我还有独一无二的色情刊物的收藏品
I have, upstairs,\nthe most unique collection of erotica.

1193
2:07:12,910 --> 2:07:14,280
把枪扔掉 把枪扔掉
Drop the gun. Drop the gun.

1194
2:07:14,450 --> 2:07:18,580
另外 我还可以安排你去参加死刑执行
Also, moreover, I can arrange\nfor you to attend executions.

1195
2:07:18,740 --> 2:07:21,740
并不是每个人知道电椅是漆成黄色的
Not everybody knows\nthe chair is painted yellow.

1196
2:07:24,240 --> 2:07:25,620
来人救命啊
Somebody help!

1197
2:08:31,200 --> 2:08:32,870
啊！！
Aargh! Agh!

1198
2:08:33,870 --> 2:08:35,870
很疼 先生
That hurts, sir.

1199
2:08:36,040 --> 2:08:38,620
我亲爱的老兄 那很的很疼
That hurts atrociously, my dear fellow.

1200
2:08:49,290 --> 2:08:51,290
老天爷
God...

1201
2:08:51,460 --> 2:08:54,540
你真的不该一直穿成这个样子
You should not continue\nin this fashion, really.

1202
2:09:25,210 --> 2:09:27,000
滚出去！
Get out!

1203
2:09:27,160 --> 2:09:28,830
从这里滚出去！
Get out of here!

1204
2:11:38,090 --> 2:11:41,460
我听到了孩子们的欢声笑语
What I heard then was\nthe melody of children at play.

1205
2:11:41,630 --> 2:11:07,630
除此之外 没有别的
Nothing but that.

1206
2:11:46,000 --> 2:11:49,170
让我心灰意冷的并不是
And I knew that\nthe hopelessly poignant thing...

1207
2:11:49,340 --> 2:11:52,170
洛丽塔不在我身边
..was not Lolita's absence from my side...

1208
2:11:53,840 --> 2:11:56,880
而是这里的欢笑声中没有她
..but the absence other voice\nfrom that chorus.

